      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical release-controlled with documented QA procedures and regression test suite; FDA in-house solver subject to FDA software QA SOP.",
      "rationale": "Both simulation platforms (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 and FDA in-house FEA code) are under formal version control. Regression test suites are executed at each release. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for a medium model-risk COU."
