      "rationale": "A three-level mesh convergence study was performed on the pedicle screw construct geometry. GCI values ranged from 1.2% to 3.7% across QoIs. The fine mesh was selected for production runs. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
