      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activity uses the same construct geometry, material, and test standard as the COU; validation domain overlaps with the intended use domain.",
      "rationale": "The validation activity directly replicates the COU: same 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screw, same ASTM F1717 test configuration, same Ti-6Al-4V rod material. The validation domain is essentially coincident with the COU domain, providing high relevance. The single-condition limitation (Test conditions factor) is the only identified gap."
